ite, K. D., 1999: Introduction to River Ice. At the COMET Hydrometeorology 99-2 Course, US Army Cold Regions Research & Engineering Laboratory. (PPT available at http://www.comet.ucar.edu/ class/hydromet/index.htm)Yeston, J., Coontz, R., Smith, J., Ash, C., Introduction to special issue, a thirsty world (2006) Science, 31, p. 1067","Byun, H.-R.; Dept. of Environmental Atmospheric Sciences, Pukyong National Univ., Daeyeon-3 dong, Namku, Busan 608-737, South Korea; email: hrbyun@pknu.ac.kr",,,,,,,,19767633,,,,"English","Asia Pac. J. Atmos. Sci",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-44949172632
